<ListItem [className]="'am-checkbox-item ' + (disabled ? 'am-checkbox-item-disabled' : '')"

          [thumb]="checkbox"
          (onClick)="onCheckboxClick($event)"
>
  <ng-content></ng-content>
</ListItem>
<ng-template #checkbox>
  <label Checkbox
         [name]="name"
         [value]="value"
         [checked]="checked"
         [disabled]="disabled"
         (onChange)="change($event)"
  >
  </label>
</ng-template>

<List class="{{subMenuPrefixCls}}" style="padding: 0">
  <ListItem *ngFor="let dataItem of subMenuData; let i = index;"
            key="i"
            [className]="getClass(dataItem)"
            [extra]="extra"
  >
    {{dataItem.label}}

    <ng-template #extra>
      <label Radio
             *ngIf="!multiSelect"
             [checked]="selected(dataItem)"
             [disabled]="dataItem.disabled"
             (onChange)="onClick(dataItem)"
      >
      </label>
      <label Checkbox
             *ngIf="multiSelect"
             [checked]="selected(dataItem)"
             [disabled]="dataItem.disabled"
             (onChange)="onClick(dataItem)"
      >
      </label>
    </ng-template>
  </ListItem>
</List>
